Program for Practice
1. Program to check whether given Integer is Perfect Square or not
2. Program to reverse the digits of an number
3. Program to reverse the first half of array elements
4. Program to reverse the second half of array elements
5. Program to Sort the Elements in ascending order
6. Program to Sort the Elements in descending order
7. Program to sort half of the Array elements in ascending order and next half in descending order
8. Program to Merging two arrays
9. Find the location of given sub string in a String
10. Count the occurrences of given substring in a String
